        "question": "<strong>Sarah (22)</strong> saved $10,000 for a house down payment. In 2017, she heard Bitcoin would reach $100,000...<br><br><strong>December 2017 Peak:</strong> $35,000<br><strong>December 2018 Crash:</strong> $8,000<br><strong>Net Loss After Panic Sell:</strong> -$2,000<br><br><strong>Today's Question:</strong> When are alternative investments smart\u2014and when are they speculative mistakes?"
      },
      "headerColor": "amber"
    },
